            bindings = <
       &kp Q            &kp W            &kp E                &kp R              &kp T          &kp Y        &kp U          &kp I         &kp O        &kp P
       &hml LGUI A      &hml LALT S      &hml LCTRL D         &hml LSHFT F       &kp G          &kp H        &hmr RSHFT J   &hmr RCTRL K  &hmr RALT L  &hmr RGUI SEMICOLON
&none  &hml LEFT_GUI Z  &hml LEFT_ALT X  &hml LEFT_CONTROL C  &hml LEFT_SHIFT V  &kp B          &kp N        &kp M          &kp COMMA     &kp DOT      &kp FSLH             &none
