        &kp HASH     &kp DOLLAR  &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp GRAVE    &kp MINUS        &kp KP_NUMBER_4  &kp KP_NUMBER_5  &kp KP_NUMBER_6  &kp KP_PLUS
&trans  &kp PERCENT  &kp CARET   &kp LEFT_BRACKET      &kp RIGHT_BRACKET      &kp TILDE    &kp AMPERSAND    &kp KP_NUMBER_1  &kp KP_NUMBER_2  &kp KP_NUMBER_3  &kp BSLH      &trans
                                 &trans                &trans                 &trans       &kp KP_NUMBER_0  &trans           &trans
            >;
